# mcp-config-wizard

> ğŸ§™ Easily configure MCP servers through a beautiful interactive CLI â€” no complex commands needed.

[![Python 3.8+](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.8+-blue.svg)](https://www.python.org/downloads/)
