## ğŸ› ï¸ Development

### Clone and Setup

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/mcp-config-wizard.git
cd mcp-config-wizard
uv sync
```

### Run Locally

```bash
uv run mcp-wizard
```

### Build Package

```bash
uv build
```

### Publish to PyPI

```bash
uv publish
```

